Token.Abstract: A service which is used to record Amazon Mobile Analytics events

Parameter.Name: request
Parameter.Abstract: A container for the necessary parameters to execute the PutEvents service method.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An instance of BFTask. On successful execution, task.result will be nil. On failed execution, task.error may contain an NSError with AWSMobileAnalyticsERSErrorDomain domian and the following error code: AWSMobileAnalyticsERSErrorBadRequest.
